    "When enabled, cutoff that overlaps with retreat movement is ignored (forward: early cutoff, reverse: late cutoff)." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "有効にすると、退避移動と重なるカットオフを無視します（順再生: 序盤を無視、逆再生: 終盤を無視）。"
          }
        }
